tags.wheelchair:description: Sisään pääsee, mutta ei paikkaan jossa pääsee tilaamaan ruokaa. You can get in but not to the place where you order you order.
Invavessa löytyy kokoushuoneen takaa! / The wheelchair accessible restroom is behind the meeting room! Ask help from waiter.

There are ramps to the restaurant when coming from Aleksanterinkatu.
There are 2 wheelchair accessible toilets for small(ish) wheelchairs in different sides of the restaurant: there are 3 steps between these 2 halves.
